<TEXT>
sixtysix drug smugglers and four 
burglars have been hanged in tehran and 19 other cities state 
radio reported 
the executions thursday bring the total number of reported 
executions of drug smugglers in recent months to 379 
the tehran radio broadcast monitored in nicosia said 17 of the 
smugglers were hanged in the capital 
several of those executed also were convicted of armed 
resistance gun smuggling mischief creating panic and 
involvement in murder the radio said 
authorities also confiscated 18935 pounds of opium 1757 
pounds of heroin and 16440 pounds of morphine from the smugglers 
the radio reported 
a draconian new law that took effect jan 21 carries the death 
sentence for possession of even small quantities of drugs the new 
crackdown is an effort to combat rampant drug addiction in the 
country 
</TEXT>
