as more personnel to analyze photographic and radar data 
the kh11 takes high resolution photographs and the lacrosse 
uses radar for surveillance at night and through clouds 
boren told the times that if the bush administration continues 
with the plan not to improve satellite surveillance it could 
greatly damage the presidents relationship with the senate 
