the exposition calibre 89 has been viewed by nearly 10000 
potential buyers and watch fans on a presale world tour with stops 
in europe the united states japan hong kong and singapore 
made by patek philippe the geneva watchmaking company to mark 
its 150th anniversary the 18carat 34inchdiameter gold case 
packs 68 springs 126 jewels and 332 screws 
